amesmarket

Class TransGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.TransGrid

  • public class TransGrid
extends java.lang.Object
    Transmission grid setup and formulations of rudimentary matrics in preparing for DCOPFJ.java. The matrix notations and Eq numebering follow DC-OPF paper. DC-OPF paper: Junjie Sun and Leigh Tesfatsion, (2006) "DC OPF Formulation and Solution Using QuadProgJ", ISU Econ Working Paper Series #06014 Example of what contains in nodeData and branchData.

    NodeData 

      NN    penaltyCoeff
  3     0.05

    BranchData 

    //From  To      MaxCap  Reactance
  1     2       100     0.08
  1     3       150     0.12
  2     3       120     0.05
